{'title': 'Duisburg‘da Hanau Katliam Eylemi!', 'description': 'DUISBURG|19.02.2023|\xa0Almanya’nın Hanau kentinde ırkçı bir saldırı sonucu 19 Mart 2020’de katledilen ...', 'type': 'article', 'time': '2023-02-19T99:00:00-04:00', 'author': ['muhabirberkay'], 'images': ['https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7587-620x330.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImagegFcZeS-100x75.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImagew7j7fT-100x75.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImage7hzNpd-100x75.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImage1B14FJ-100x75.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7584-100x56.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7580-56x100.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7583-100x56.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImagesVsN14-75x100.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImage0T0V1h-75x100.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7585-56x100.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7586-56x100.jpg', 'https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7587-100x56.jpg'], 'text': '![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7587-620x330.jpg)\n\nDUISBURG|19.02.2023| Almanya’nın Hanau kentinde ırkçı bir saldırı sonucu 19Mart 2020’de katledilen Gökhan Gültekin, Sedat Gürbüz, Said Nesar Hashemi,Mercedes Kierpacz, Hamza Kenan Kurtović, Vili Viorel Păun, Fatih Saraçoğlu,Ferhat Unvar ve Kaloyan Velkov için Duisburg’da anma etkinliğigerçekleştirildi.\n\nBugün saat 14:00’da Duisburg Karşı Duruyor (Duisburg Stellt Sich Quer)platformunun çağrısı ile bir mitüng gerçekleştirildi. ‘‘Affetmiyoruz,Unutmuyoruz‘‘ sloganıyla, şehir merkezinde bulunan König Heinrich Platz’dagerçekleştirilen mitingde katliamı kınayan konuşmalar gerçekleştirildi.\n\nMitingin ardından ATİF, YDG, AGİF, SKB, NEUE FRAU, ZORA, ROTES RUHRGEBIET,INTERNATIONALE JUGEND RUHR, PRIDE REBELLION ve STUDENTS FOR FUTURE gibiantifaşist örgütlerin katılımıyla bir yürüyüş gerçekleştirildi. Yürüyüşesnasında “Irkçılığa hayır”, “Faşizme karşı omuz omuza”, “Unutmadık,Unutturmayacağız” ve “Dayanışmayı yükseltelim” sloganları atıldı.\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImagegFcZeS-100x75.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/tempimagegfczes)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImagew7j7fT-100x75.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/tempimagew7j7ft)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImage7hzNpd-100x75.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/tempimage7hznpd)\n\n\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImage1B14FJ-100x75.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/tempimage1b14fj)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7584-100x56.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/img_7584)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7580-56x100.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/img_7580-2)\n\n\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7583-100x56.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/img_7583)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImagesVsN14-75x100.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/tempimagesvsn14)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/tempImage0T0V1h-75x100.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/tempimage0t0v1h)\n\n\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7585-56x100.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/img_7585)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7586-56x100.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/img_7586)\n\n[![](https://www.atik-online.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_7587-100x56.jpg)](https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi/img_7587)\n\n', 'categories': ['Avrupa', 'Haberler', 'Manset'], 'source': 'https://www.atik-online.net/blog/duisburgda-hanau-katliam-eylemi'}